Third-party data attribution
============================

caniemail
---------

The HTML client-compatibility feature of this package uses the caniemail
email-client support dataset:

  https://www.caniemail.com
  https://github.com/shellscape/caniemail

The caniemail data is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
International license (CC-BY-4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Modifications: the copy bundled as this package's test fixture
(tests/Fixtures/caniemail-features.json) is a snapshot of the upstream
dataset with the per-feature "test_results_url" fields removed; it is
otherwise unmodified. The dataset a host application syncs at runtime via
`php artisan htmlcheck:sync-data` is fetched from upstream unmodified.
